       <div class="vt-postcontent">
       good job!
<br />just some notes:
<br />
<br />. you can't activate Stora with no drive inserted, the software won't allow it
<br />. you can use the storaunlock or any of the hack to get root access to the Stora
<br />
<br />I know you said you had just activated the stora, but did you notice if you lost any data in the process? I'm not sure switching from raid1 to raid0 in this way will preserve all the data, probably yes though...
<br />If you have some time, you could write a simple wiki page to summarize the process and put a reference to this post for comments.
       </div> 
       
